    "body": "@redsquirrel although I agree with your concerns about \"having to scroll up\", I think it is much easier to verify the semantics for a group of functions that all have a certain modifier than to check that the modifier is present in every single function.\nIn the end, this all boils down to the fact that authors have to write contracts responsibly. The inheritance feature can also be exploited to pull in effects in a non-local way.\n",
