    "body": "@chriseth Would you recommend people use modifier areas like this?\n\n```\ncontract Foo {\n    modifier a() {}\n    modifier b() {}\n\n    function x() a() {}\n    function y() b() {}\n    function z() a() b() {}\n}\n```\n\n_becomes_\n\n```\ncontract Foo {\n    modifier a() {}\n    modifier b() {}\n\n    using modifier a() {\n        function x() {}\n        function z() b() {}\n    }\n\n    function y() b() {}\n}\n```\n\nOne would have to pick and choose which modifiers get areas and which would have to stay inline. Right?\n",
